Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.03,0:10:49.49,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs13\pos(245,103)}已经适应日本了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.03,0:10:49.49,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs13\pos(230,123)}看到这个回答老师有点担心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.03,0:10:49.49,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(197,84)}吉井明久的回答
